hel Stein</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Rebekah M Padilla</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Gregory Wynn</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2021Mar1 | Cureus, Vol. 16</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.7759/cureus.13627">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1007/s00247-020-04775-1"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00247-020-04775-1">Virtual endoluminal aortic root views determined at coronary CT angiography — an important tool for improving anomalous coronary artery visualization and surgical planning</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Vijetha V. Maller</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Harris L. Cohen</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Umar Boston</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Sandeep Sainathan</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Christopher J. Knott-Craig</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">5 September 2020 | Pediatric Radiology, Vol. 51, No. 2</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00247-020-04775-1">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1007/978-981-15-6755-1_9"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-981-15-6755-1_9">Radiological Review of Coronary Artery Anomalies</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Archita Goel</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Bhavana Nagabhushana Reddy</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-Co